<item>
  <title>Kaggle CLI 控制 Notebook：本地寫、雲端跑、拉回結果</title>
  <link>https://ch1nv.github.io/luchinwei/notes/tech/kaggle/kaggle-cli-notebook-workflow.html</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 




<section id="目標工作流" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="目標工作流">目標工作流</h2>
<p>這篇整理 Kaggle 原生 CLI 的常用指令。目標是讓 Kaggle Notebook 的使用方式接近 Git workflow：</p>
<pre class="text"><code>本機 repo / notebook
  -&gt; 修改 .ipynb
  -&gt; kaggle kernels push
  -&gt; Kaggle 雲端執行 GPU / CPU notebook
  -&gt; kaggle kernels status 查狀態
  -&gt; kaggle kernels output 抓回 submission.csv / log
  -&gt; kaggle competitions submit 提交結果</code></pre>
</section>
<section id="先備條件" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="先備條件">先備條件</h2>
<p>安裝 Kaggle CLI：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb2" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb2-1">pip install kaggle</span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>設定 API token。傳統 <code>kaggle.json</code> 通常放在：</p>
<pre class="text"><code>C:\Users\&lt;你的 Windows 使用者&gt;\.kaggle\kaggle.json</code></pre>
<p>內容格式：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb4" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode json code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode json"><span id="cb4-1"><span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">{</span></span>
<span id="cb4-2">  <span class="dt" style="color: #AD0000;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">"username"</span><span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">:</span> <span class="st" style="color: #20794D;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">"你的_kaggle_username"</span><span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">,</span></span>
<span id="cb4-3">  <span class="dt" style="color: #AD0000;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">"key"</span><span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">:</span> <span class="st" style="color: #20794D;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">"你的_api_key"</span></span>
<span id="cb4-4"><span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">}</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>新版 Kaggle CLI 也可能要求用環境變數：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb5" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb5-1"><span class="va" style="color: #111111;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">$env</span><span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">:</span><span class="va" style="color: #111111;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">KAGGLE_API_TOKEN</span> <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">=</span> <span class="st" style="color: #20794D;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">"你的_api_key"</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>確認 CLI 可用：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb6" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb6-1">kaggle <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">--</span>version</span></code></pre></div></div>
</section>
<section id="git-類比" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="git-類比">Git 類比</h2>
<table class="caption-top table">
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 33%">
<col style="width: 33%">
<col style="width: 33%">
</colgroup>
<thead>
<tr class="header">
<th>Git 習慣</th>
<th>Kaggle CLI</th>
<th>用途</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr class="odd">
<td><code>git push</code></td>
<td><code>kaggle kernels push -p .</code></td>
<td>把本地 notebook 推到 Kaggle，並觸發雲端執行</td>
</tr>
<tr class="even">
<td><code>git status</code></td>
<td><code>kaggle kernels status owner/kernel-slug</code></td>
<td>查看 notebook 執行狀態</td>
</tr>
<tr class="odd">
<td><code>git pull</code></td>
<td><code>kaggle kernels pull owner/kernel-slug -p .</code></td>
<td>把 Kaggle 網頁上的 notebook 拉回本地</td>
</tr>
<tr class="even">
<td>下載 artifacts</td>
<td><code>kaggle kernels output owner/kernel-slug -p outputs --force</code></td>
<td>抓回 <code>submission.csv</code>、log、模型檔等輸出</td>
</tr>
<tr class="odd">
<td>發佈結果</td>
<td><code>kaggle competitions submit ...</code></td>
<td>提交比賽 submission</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</section>
<section id="kernel-metadata" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="kernel-metadata">Kernel metadata</h2>
<p>要用 <code>kaggle kernels push</code>，資料夾中需要有 <code>kernel-metadata.json</code>。</p>
<p>範例：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb7" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode json code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode json"><span id="cb7-1"><span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;
