<section id="最常用工作流" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="最常用工作流">最常用工作流</h2>
<section id="本地修改-notebook" class="level3">
<h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="本地修改-notebook">1. 本地修改 notebook</h3>
<p>例如修改：</p>
<pre class="text"><code>s6e6_starter.ipynb</code></pre>
</section>
<section id="推到-kaggle-雲端執行" class="level3">
<h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="推到-kaggle-雲端執行">2. 推到 Kaggle 雲端執行</h3>
<p>在有 <code>kernel-metadata.json</code> 的資料夾執行：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb9" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb9-1">kaggle kernels push <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>p <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">.</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>成功時會看到類似：</p>
<pre class="text"><code>Kernel version 2 successfully pushed. Please check progress at https://www.kaggle.com/code/&lt;owner&gt;/&lt;kernel-slug&gt;</code></pre>
</section>
<section id="查執行狀態" class="level3">
<h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="查執行狀態">3. 查執行狀態</h3>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb11" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb11-1">kaggle kernels status your-kaggle-username<span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">/</span>s6e6-starter</span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>常見狀態：</p>
<ul>
<li><code>KernelWorkerStatus.RUNNING</code>: 正在跑。</li>
<li><code>KernelWorkerStatus.COMPLETE</code>: 跑完，可以抓 output。</li>
<li><code>KernelWorkerStatus.ERROR</code>: 執行失敗，要看 log。</li>
<li><code>KernelWorkerStatus.CANCELLED</code>: 被取消。</li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="抓回-output" class="level3">
<h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="抓回-output">4. 抓回 output</h3>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb12" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb12-1">kaggle kernels output your-kaggle-username<span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">/</span>s6e6-starter <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>p outputs <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">--</span>force</span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>下載後通常會看到：</p>
<pre class="text"><code>outputs/
  submission.csv
  &lt;kernel-slug&gt;.log</code></pre>
</section>
<section id="提交-submission" class="level3">
<h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="提交-submission">5. 提交 submission</h3>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb14" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb14-1">kaggle competitions submit <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>c playground-series-s6e6 <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>f outputs\submission<span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">.</span><span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">csv</span> <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>m <span class="st" style="color: #20794D;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">"starter submission"</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
</section>
<section id="查看提交紀錄" class="level3">
<h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="查看提交紀錄">6. 查看提交紀錄</h3>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb15" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb15-1">kaggle competitions submissions <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>c playground-series-s6e6</span></code></pre></div></div>
</section>
</section>
<section id="常用-kaggle-cli-指令" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="常用-kaggle-cli-指令">常用 Kaggle CLI 指令</h2>
<section id="notebook-kernel" class="level3">
<h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="notebook-kernel">Notebook / Kernel</h3>
<p>列出自己的 kernels：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb16" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb16-1">kaggle kernels list <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">--</span>mine</span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>推送目前資料夾到 Kaggle：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb17" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb17-1">kaggle kernels push <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>p <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">.</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>查 kernel 狀態：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb18" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb18-1">kaggle kernels status owner<span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">/</span>kernel-slug</span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>抓回 kernel output：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb19" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb19-1">kaggle kernels output owner<span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">/</span>kernel-slug <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>p outputs <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">--</span>force</span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>把 Kaggle 上的 kernel 拉回本地：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb20" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb20-1">kaggle kernels pull owner<span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">/</span>kernel-slug <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>p <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">.</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>只有當你在 Kaggle 網頁上直接改 notebook，才比較需要 <code>pull</code>。如果你的主工作區在本機，通常只需要 <code>push</code>、<code>status</code>、<code>output</code>。</p>
</section>
<section id="competitions" class="level3">
<h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="competitions">Competitions</h3>
<p>列出比賽：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb21" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb21-1">kaggle competitions list</span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>下載比賽資料：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb22" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb22-1">kaggle competitions download <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>c playground-series-s6e6 <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>p <span class="kw" style="color: #003B4F;
background-color: null;
font-weight: bold;
font-style: inherit;">data</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>提交結果：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb23" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb23-1">kaggle competitions submit <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>c playground-series-s6e6 <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>f outputs\submission<span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">.</span><span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">csv</span> <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>m <span class="st" style="color: #20794D;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">"message"</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>查看提交紀錄：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb24" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb24-1">kaggle competitions submissions <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>c playground-series-s6e6</span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>查看 leaderboard：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb25" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb25-1">kaggle competitions leaderboard <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>c playground-series-s6e6 <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">--</span>show</span></code></pre></div></div>
</section>
<section id="datasets" class="level3">
<h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="datasets">Datasets</h3>
<p>下載 dataset：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb26" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb26-1">kaggle datasets download <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>d owner<span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">/</span>dataset-slug <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>p <span class="kw" style="color: #003B4F;
background-color: null;
font-weight: bold;
font-style: inherit;">data</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>列出 datasets：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb27" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb27-1">kaggle datasets list <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>s keyword</span></code></pre></div></div>
</section>
</section>
<section id="notebook-裡讀比賽資料" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="notebook-裡讀比賽資料">Notebook 裡讀比賽資料</h2>
<p>如果在 Kaggle Notebook 雲端執行，competition source 會掛載在：</p>
<pre class="text"><code>/kaggle/input/&lt;competition-slug&gt;</code></pre>
<p>例如：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb29" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode python code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode python"><span id="cb29-1"><span class="im" style="color: #00769E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">from</span> pathlib <span class="im" style="color: #00769E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">import</span> Path</span>
<span id="cb29-2"><span class="im" style="color: #00769E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">import</span> pandas <span class="im" style="color: #00769E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">as</span> pd</span>
<span id="cb29-3"></span>
<span id="cb29-4">DATA_DIR <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">=</span> Path(<span class="st" style="color: #20794D;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">"/kaggle/input/playground-series-s6e6"</span>)</span>
<span id="cb29-5">train <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">=</span> pd.read_csv(DATA_DIR <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">/</span> <span class="st" style="color: #20794D;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">"train.csv"</span>)</span>
<span id="cb29-6">test <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">=</span> pd.read_csv(DATA_DIR <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">/</span> <span class="st" style="color: #20794D;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">"test.csv"</span>)</span>
<span id="cb29-7">sample_submission <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">=</span> pd.read_csv(DATA_DIR <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">/</span> <span class="st" style="color: #20794D;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">"sample_submission.csv"</span>)</span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>如果想讓 notebook 同時支援本機和 Kaggle，可以寫 fallback：</p>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb30" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode python code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode python"><span id="cb30-1"><span class="im" style="color: #00769E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">from</span> pathlib <span class="im" style="color: #00769E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">import</span> Path</span>
<span id="cb30-2"><span class="im" style="color: #00769E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">import</span> kagglehub</span>
<span id="cb30-3"></span>
<span id="cb30-4">COMPETITION <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">=</span> <span class="st" style="color: #20794D;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">"playground-series-s6e6"</span></span>
<span id="cb30-5"></span>
<span id="cb30-6">kaggle_input <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">=</span> Path(<span class="ss" style="color: #20794D;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">f"/kaggle/input/</span><span class="sc" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">{</span>COMPETITION<span class="sc" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">}</span><span class="ss" style="color: #20794D;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">"</span>)</span>
<span id="cb30-7"><span class="cf" style="color: #003B4F;
background-color: null;
font-weight: bold;
font-style: inherit;">if</span> kaggle_input.exists():</span>
<span id="cb30-8">    data_dir <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">=</span> kaggle_input</span>
<span id="cb30-9"><span class="cf" style="color: #003B4F;
background-color: null;
font-weight: bold;
font-style: inherit;">else</span>:</span>
<span id="cb30-10">    data_dir <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">=</span> Path(kagglehub.competition_download(COMPETITION))</span></code></pre></div></div>
</section>
<section id="建議資料夾結構" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="建議資料夾結構">建議資料夾結構</h2>
<pre class="text"><code>my-kaggle-project/
  kernel-metadata.json
  s6e6_starter.ipynb
  outputs/
    submission.csv
    s6e6-starter.log
  data/
  README.md</code></pre>
<p>通常不要 commit：</p>
<pre class="text"><code>.kaggle/
outputs/
data/
*.zip</code></pre>
</section>
<section id="一組完整日常指令" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="一組完整日常指令">一組完整日常指令</h2>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb33" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode powershell code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode powershell"><span id="cb33-1"><span class="co" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;"># 本地改完 notebook 後，推到 Kaggle 跑</span></span>
<span id="cb33-2">kaggle kernels push <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>p <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">.</span></span>
<span id="cb33-3"></span>
<span id="cb33-4"><span class="co" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;"># 等它跑完</span></span>
<span id="cb33-5">kaggle kernels status your-kaggle-username<span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">/</span>s6e6-starter</span>
<span id="cb33-6"></span>
<span id="cb33-7"><span class="co" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;"># 抓回 submission 和 log</span></span>
<span id="cb33-8">kaggle kernels output your-kaggle-username<span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">/</span>s6e6-starter <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>p outputs <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">--</span>force</span>
<span id="cb33-9"></span>
<span id="cb33-10"><span class="co" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;"># 提交到比賽</span></span>
<span id="cb33-11">kaggle competitions submit <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>c playground-series-s6e6 <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>f outputs\submission<span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">.</span><span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">csv</span> <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>m <span class="st" style="color: #20794D;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">"first baseline"</span></span>
<span id="cb33-12"></span>
<span id="cb33-13"><span class="co" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;"># 看提交紀錄</span></span>
<span id="cb33-14">kaggle competitions submissions <span class="op" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-</span>c playground-series-s6e6</span></code></pre></div></div>
</section>
<section id="小提醒" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="小提醒">小提醒</h2>
<ul>
<li><code>kaggle kernels push -p .</code> 會根據目前資料夾的 <code>kernel-metadata.json</code> 推送。</li>
<li><code>status</code> 和 <code>output</code> 要用 <code>owner/kernel-slug</code>，也就是 Kaggle notebook URL 裡的 owner 和 slug。</li>
<li>如果 notebook 是 private，通常自己的 token 可以存取，但別人的 token 不行。</li>
<li>如果 <code>output</code> 抓不到，先確認 <code>status</code> 是 <code>COMPLETE</code>。</li>
<li>如果 notebook 在 Kaggle 上失敗，先抓 output 或到網頁看 log。</li>
<li>本地是主版本時，盡量不要在 Kaggle 網頁上直接改 notebook；如果改了，要記得 <code>kaggle kernels pull</code> 拉回來，避免版本分叉。</li>
</ul>


